        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 18 at 7:27PM EDT until July 18 at 7:45PM EDT by NWS Peachtree City GA</headline>
        <description>At 727 PM EDT, a severe thunderstorm was located over Pendergrass, or
near Jefferson, moving northeast at 55 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and nickel size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Winder, Braselton, Auburn, Hoschton, Carl, Chestnut Mountain, Road
Atlanta-Lanier Speedway, County Line, Thompsons Mill, and Chateau
Elan.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
